    {
        "DisplayName": "Module Name",
        "Category": "Module",
        "Description": "The module to load - enter the .mod file's name WITHOUT the .mod extension (e.g. for a file named MyWorld.mod, enter MyWorld, not MyWorld.mod). Case-sensitive. Upload the module into userdata/modules (and any required haks into userdata/hak, custom .tlk into userdata/tlk) before starting. The default 'ChangeMe' exists only so the first SteamCMD install can run past this required field - replace it with your real module name before starting the server.",
